entries.femaleVariant: This is a joke! A fuckin' joke! Sendin' a cop to a neighborhood like that... a year before retirement!
More like a goddamn death sentence. Tellin' you, Lena's about to crack.
Few months in Northside, she'll blast herself.
Helluva good cop, too. Got her heart in the right place. Why they gotta do her like this?
Eddies, choom. Better to send someone who's on their way out already.
Man, you gotta be a real coldhearted bastard to think that way 'bout Lena... 'bout anyone.
Yeah, but that's the system. Ain't got a better one.
